  "body": "This issue is meant to track the `experimentalAddHardhatNetworkMessageTraceHook` feature, mainly to allow anyone using it to subscribe to this and know if there are any changes to it.\r\n\r\nSome open questions about this feature:\r\n\r\n- Is it useful? Who's using it and how? How can it be improved?\r\n- Is the level of abstraction right, or should it be at a lower or higher level?\r\n- In case it's fine as it is, what does it need to happen to stabilize it?",
